My boys’ favorite soup! 🌽 Sweet corn pork ribs soup. We added carrot and potatoes for more flavor.

May wanna try to add chicken bones to the soup together with the pork ribs to enhance the soup’s taste next time.

Ingredients:
Sweet Corn
Pork Spare Ribs
Dried scallops
Red dates
Carrots
Potatoes
Wolfberries
Yellow onion
Water
Salt (Optional)
